quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,127,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,128,"“Ana nkutaŵa pachikwesya palipose pakusalala nyumba syeleuleu mwamasanje (pagamba kusaka kulosya machili ngaŵa syagonamo)?”"
  26,129,"“Ni nkulitaŵila makome gamakulungwakulungwa nti chisawu tinnonjele?”"
  28,73,"Soni mwa ukoto Wakwe, ŵam’biichiile jenumanja chilo ni muusi kuti ntulalilejemo (nchilomo), ni kuti nsosejesoseje umbone Wakwe (muusi), ni kuti jenumanja m’beje ŵakutogolela."
  28,74,"Soni (kumbuchilani) lisiku lyatachaŵilanga ŵanganyao (Allah) basi ni tachiti: “Ali kwapi akumwanganya nao aŵala ŵamwaliji nkulitwanjila?”"
  28,75,"Ni tuchikoposya kuumila mu nkutula uliose mboni (jakuutendela umboni nkutulao) ni tuchiti: “Ikani nao umboni wenu.” Basi ni tachimanyilila yanti: Yakuona ni ya Allah (Jikape), ni ichasokonechela ŵanganyao (isanamu) yaŵaliji nkuisepelela."
  29,40,"Basi jwalijose (mwa ŵanganyao) twankwembekenye ni sambi syakwe. Basi ŵane mwa jamanjao pana ŵatwatumichisye chimbunga cha sakalawe, ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵawakwembekenye n’gumilo (waipotesi), ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵatwatitimisye nalyo litaka, soni ŵane mwa ŵanganyao pana ŵatwamisyisye. Sano Allah nganijuŵa jwanti ni kwatenda lupuso ŵanganyao, nambo kuti ŵanyao ni ŵaŵaliji nkulitenda lupuso achimisyene."
  29,41,"Chilandanyo cha aŵala ŵalitendele jwinepe jwangaŵaga Allah kuŵa kaligoselo, chili chisawu nyangata jwalitendele nyumba (ja lundandambuli jangaŵa nkun’gosa kuchitukuta namuno mbepo), soni chisimu naga nyumba jangali machili ninyumba ja nyangata, ingaŵe ŵanganyao ŵamanyililaga."
  29,42,"Chisimu Allah jukuimanya ichindu iliyose yaakuilumbanjila ŵanganyao kunneka Jwalakwe, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  30,19,"Jwalakwe jukasakoposyaga chaumi kuumila mu chachiwe, ni koposya chachiwe kuumila mu chaumi, ni kulisyusya litaka panyuma pakuwa kwakwe, soni iyyoyopeyo tinchikoposyedwa ŵanganyammwe (m’malembe ni kuŵa ni umi soni)."
  30,20,"Soni mu imanyilo Yakwe (yakulosya uchimbichimbi ni ukombosi Wakwe) ni yanti, ŵan’gumbile jenumanja kuumila mwitaka, kaneka jenumanja ni kuŵa ŵandu ŵankwenela (posepose)."
  30,21,"Soni mu imanyilo Yakwe (yakulosya ukoto Wakwe) ni yanti, an’guumbiile ŵanganyammwe kuumila mwa jenumanja achimisyene achiŵammakwenu kuti ntulalileje kwa jamanjao, ni aŵisile chilikati chenu chinonyelo kwisa soni chanasa. Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana imanyilo kwa ŵandu ŵaakuchetelelaga."
  31,4,"Aŵala ŵaakwimikaga Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, nambo soni ya Akhera jamanjao akasakulupilila kusyesyene."
  31,5,"Ŵele ŵanganyao ali pachongoko chakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao, soni ŵanyao ni ŵali ŵakupunda."
  31,6,"Soni chilikati cha ŵandu pana jwaakusumaga ngani syachanache kuti jusokonesye (nasyo ŵandu) kwitala lya Allah mwangali umanyilisi, ni jukulitendaga soni chipongwe (litala lya Allah kwisa soni ma Ȃya Gakwe). Ŵanganyao akwete kupata ilagasyo yakwalusya."